data.event: Tourist attractions in Sinnar include: Jogeshwary and Bhairavnath temple: located in Patole village about 7 kilometres southeast of Sinnar Satimata-Samatdada Temple in Vadangali Pataleshwar Temple: located in Chas-Nalwadi, 27 km From Sinnar Bhojapur Dam: located near Chas, 26 km from Sinnar, built in 1972
